                           Other Software Released@1
                           -----------------------

Starbase V1.2 is a isometric building game like@3 "Utopia"@1,  with space  ships
to build and to wipe out the four@3 "neighbours"@1 next to your base.
 
Diamond  Challenge  V0.9ß  is a platform game  where  you  have  to  collect
several  amount  of  diamonds to finish a level.  Some baddies  and  special
tools make it harder, of course.

The  game is freeware,  but the level editor is shareware and can be ordered
from me, like Arkanos.

Colonization  Map  Editor  V1.0 is just a map  editor  for  the  great  game
@2"Colonization"@1 from Microprose. It's giftware.


